    "aresKeywords": "specialised plant cells, root hair cell, guard cells, stomata, xylem vessel, phloem sieve tube, palisade mesophyll, cell specialisation, plant cell structure, form and function, lignin, chloroplasts, water transport, sugar transport, absorption, transpiration, Turkana drought adaptation, Kericho humid climate, bean seedling, Match-the-Card, CER frame, cumulative model, driving question board, cell biology Grade 10, KICD CBC Biology"
